CS:GO VERSION
THIS IS A PORT OF A CSGO MAP I DID NOT CREATE THIS!



A map for the MAPEADORES ZOMBIE APOCALYPSE Mapping Contest!

Uptop an ancient mountain lies a Sanctuary of hope. Due to unforseen consequences, the holy land has been infected by a sinister plague.
Triggering the altar within the Sanctuary should be sufficient to wipe out the plague.

The map features:
-A beautiful marble castle to shoot zombies (or chop humans into bits!)
-Varied difficulty defense points
-Engaging zombie teleports to keep them in the action
-Souls-genre ambient music, matching the vibe of the map
-No bullshit, items, lasers or bosses. Just classic ZE gameplay!

Spent a couple weeks making this with some off days. Very quickly made so I could release it on christmas, but I did put a lot of time in even if it might not show.

Please message me if you find any bugs, gameplay or otherwise.

Edit: Forgot to include the triggers on compile yesterday so redownload it. :)

This is a converted map directly from the game Counter Strike 1.6 from Counter Strike Source. I redid all the textures, I think that for the arena it is quite good. If you want to use my map in yours, please ask permission. Since the map had some lighting problems, I added special brushes that block the light, because even through the closed brushes you can still see the light at the edges. Instead of the standard textures, I made the developer's textures, so that the map weighs very little, but is good to play and does not lag. Immediately upon spawning, each player will have 35 hep.

I decided to remake this map a little bit, as I was very much reminded of the time when I played this map back in Counter-Strike 1.6, when the two teams ran to each other with the words "It's time to die!" and started mass-cutting with each other

_sText:
My first Counter-Strike map, bringing my vision of merging 1.6 and CSS's Assault together.  
The goal were simplifying/tidy up the environment and get rid of the hostage rescue mode. I like the fast paced gameplay the original Assault has but it has lots of problems that hinder the fun. Source's remake were beautiful but the place were clutter with prop and I miss the night lighting 1.6 has, so v1622 is a little bit of both with the bomb defuse twist.  

The map support up to 32 players (16 each). Has overview/radar and nav mesh.
Original map: https://gamebanana.com/mods/411571

Original map: https://gamebanana.com/mods/413217

Stages: 5
